channel.description:
This is a great template i found ages ago btw i never used so i thought i should post it here seen as i cant find it any more!!
*
Allows users who own there own private server's of runescape to have a control panel feature/website for themselves to hopefully attract more attention to their server! It requires SQL, so just run it, it will install it into your MySQL database automatically, then delete the folder named "setup" for safety reasons. Make sure you read the read me first.
